{"tid":1625840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放軟手腳係等你哋自亂","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:49:07.000Z","uid":137789,"like":58,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"537ad8ae92009f60c97dae413d5c4c3ddb6428bf","tid":1625840,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"由得你哋燒，等你哋燒到冇嘢燒，搵啲本來唔應該燒嘅嘢嚟燒，等你哋自敗，好似兩傘咁，靜，都係一種策略嚟<br />\n<br />\n三日，等你哋一鼓作氣，再而衰三而竭，佢就彼竭我盈，一嘢出嚟大包圍，你遍地開花，可能佢調返轉集中一區，逐一擊破，只要斷交通，所有人原區，佢ko一區就真係&ldquo;平亂&rdquo;咗一區<br />\n<br />\n而家佢唔出手，啲黑冇柯打又唔敢郁，除咗深夜慢慢出嚟清場，叫住啲狗唔好衝，截停啲人又冇濫捕，其他情況幾乎完全唔見狗，此為止步<br />\n<br />\n停鐵，冇so called可靠交通，所有修復工作停止，所有之前一路破壞咗好快修復返嘅，啲中間淺色嘅唔多覺嘅，因為唔修而陳設晒出嚟，有啲人天生見到啲睇落好亂嘅嘢就會頂唔順，此為製亂<br />\n<br />\n只要你士氣低，又內亂，中立嘅又唔支持，佢出嚟end game唔係冇可能"},{"pid":"a7cf7ad216b39ffb1a0827b7d1b367d5c2d5e8f2","tid":1625840,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"頂住，有冇人"},{"pid":"611bce559395d298517df301404e1841ef9cf3fa","tid":1625840,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"睇到嗎？"},{"pid":"df4750986e0924ff14d59fcd26bc4be4098b1061","tid":1625840,"uid":177339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4107ddc79f2f2b01576cd0e032d906b0b0f8f934","tid":1625840,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4750986e0924ff14d59fcd26bc4be4098b1061","tid":1625840,"uid":177339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:05:25.000Z","msg":"推，冇人睇"},{"pid":"46ef08912e2e4a2e291601cfd821efabdd886995","tid":1625840,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/2410842979171983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccnews%2Fvideos%2F2410842979171983%2F&d=cj%2BBBxPb